text: I can tell the driver to put the package at the front porch at @UPS My Choice. But I can't tell them the port code so that they can get in. I guess they will just spend more money doing drive-bys?

@Mirarkitty We do carry an option to do that! Under Driver Instructions you can enter a Gate or Security Code. Hope this helps. Please let us know if you have further questions. ^AS https://t.co/wKJHDXWGRQ
